{"id": 2430, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在买买买时都爱给自己加哪些戏？", "description": "LV 太俗 Chanel 太名媛，CELINE 低调奢华是我本人了，就，能买得起之后的我本人。（题图来自：视觉中国 ©️ Vetta）", "record_count": 1727, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201806191806269HzDKsgwm1ZJICWy.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-02T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 290304, "content": "没事，买了这个以后，另外一个咸鱼出了就好了嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371248}, {"id": 290305, "content": "qqqqqqq琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦琪琦", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1389187}, {"id": 290306, "content": "有钱可以为所欲为", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1356507}, {"id": 290307, "content": "只是在镜子里陶醉每一款都那么适合自己，无论什么种类，什么风格看中上身一试，怎样都无法阻挡我的驾驭能力。怪我过分美丽…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1375502}, {"id": 290308, "content": "平时再怎么木讷本分这时也是奥斯卡级戏精了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1329571}, {"id": 290309, "content": "北漂已经很苦了，我再不买点儿东西慰藉一下自己，怎么去跟生活战斗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 104848}, {"id": 290310, "content": "难得看上喜欢的，下次想买的时候找不到喜欢的岂不是没得用？买", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1389205}, {"id": 290311, "content": "我就是喜欢宽衣解带式中华田园风尚且视金钱如粪土的参禅仁波切本尊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666852}, {"id": 290312, "content": "那要看买的价格贵不贵了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1103595}, {"id": 290313, "content": "大型文案灵感聚集地#恨自己不是c端运营", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386953}, {"id": 290314, "content": "买了会让我心情好?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1387280}, {"id": 290316, "content": "现在不买，以后想买就再也买不到了！买！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1031737}, {"id": 290317, "content": "刚打工资", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378907}, {"id": 290319, "content": "啊 我今天只是来帮别人看的，我得回去问问他什么意见，等明天我带他他俩一起来。（只是看看而已）", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172565}, {"id": 290579, "content": "全是我的~~我全要了没看到都多适合我吗？！！他么都在召唤我啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 961285}, {"id": 290325, "content": "喜欢就买，错过了就没了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327153}, {"id": 290327, "content": "钱只是换了种形式陪伴着我…", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 818385}, {"id": 290328, "content": "你看我精挑细选的终于买到了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1389282}, {"id": 290329, "content": "就应该对自己好点，哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1389342}, {"id": 290585, "content": "上次购物应该是618", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390454}, {"id": 290331, "content": "宁可买了后悔三分钟    也不愿意买买到遗憾三年", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1324022}, {"id": 290332, "content": "自己在折扣店里搭配的衣服   买了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1324022}, {"id": 290333, "content": "这么想 这鞋至少穿两年啊 折成每个月每一天 一天才多少钱 买买买", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1381307}, {"id": 290334, "content": "买买买，对自己好点哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1389378}, {"id": 290335, "content": "安慰自己： 早买早享受，千金难买我喜欢。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1042639}, {"id": 291104, "content": "一年三百六十五天，大概可以用个两三年，平均下来每天居然不到一块钱，耶，买!", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391852}, {"id": 290337, "content": "喜欢就买咯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1389385}, {"id": 290340, "content": "难得遇到这么喜欢的，不买下次遇不到了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139557}, {"id": 290341, "content": "国产品牌价格也不低，性价比不高，少买些便宜的攒下钱买几件性价比高的正经东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1135208}, {"id": 292645, "content": "好不容易有钱了得过过瘾", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1399537}, {"id": 291110, "content": "马上就发工资了，犒劳下自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 907458}, {"id": 290343, "content": "“不要等以后想起来才后悔。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1388873}, {"id": 290344, "content": "振兴经济，从我做起~", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186803}, {"id": 290345, "content": "年轻的时候不来美美美，等老了你买还有什么用！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366073}, {"id": 296233, "content": "老子心情好 买了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423153}, {"id": 291114, "content": "太闹心了、不买今天过不去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923165}, {"id": 292138, "content": "反正也就这么多钱，不买还是把钱花完，买了勉强够生活。所以，还是买吧……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396840}, {"id": 296234, "content": "老子心情不好 买了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423153}, {"id": 290349, "content": "早买早享受，晚买晚便宜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 906246}, {"id": 290350, "content": "好不容易碰到合适的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1370155}, {"id": 290351, "content": "哎呀反正要买的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379151}, {"id": 290352, "content": "人生无常，今朝有酒今朝醉啊。当下开心最重要", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912638}, {"id": 290353, "content": "没钱 啥也买不起", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378410}, {"id": 290354, "content": "一件衣服很贵，一条裤子很贵，一条裙子很贵但是我要穿好多天的——平均下来不算贵。买", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1388967}, {"id": 290355, "content": "我这么年轻貌美，就该在这个年纪花钱买买买来衬托自己，我配得上最美的年纪里最美的一切！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1389559}, {"id": 290356, "content": "好想买书，买书浪费钱。好想买东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1383104}, {"id": 291125, "content": "本来就穷啊  买完又不会穷到哪里去  买买买", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391959}, {"id": 290360, "content": "衣服那么多 喜欢的适合的没几件 错过了就再也没有了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372057}, {"id": 290361, "content": "买了心情就会特别好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1389577}, {"id": 296254, "content": "反正都不一定能过得过明天，留着钱干嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853127}]}